Admission requirements:
Certificate of academic degree in computer science or mathematics with 120 ECTS credits in computer science and mathematics\;  
the subject proportion in Mathematics incl. Theoretical Computer Science must be at least 35 ECTS credits and in Computer Science at least 40 ECTS credits\;
Overall "satisfactory" (2.7) or among the best 70% of the graduating class

Annotation:
Application deadline 
for EU citizens: 15 January and 15 July\; 
For non-EU citizens: 15 December and 1 June
